    "description": "<p>The datasets contain wildfire risk probabilities for transmission lines in the Western Interconnect, identified only by the HIFLD dataset identifier. The dataset is generated using PNNL's WREST Tool (https://www.pnnl.gov/projects/wildfire-risk-resilience/tools/wrest). The input dataset includes HIFLD datasets on transmission lines and wildfire burn potentials and flame lengths from the PNNL RADR-FIRE Tool for 2025.</p>",
